            <p>Yet <em>another </em>version of The Elder Scrolls 5: Skyrim has arrived before The Elder Scrolls 6, with a <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/platforms/switch-2">Switch 2</a> release of Bethesda's Anniversary Edition available now for Â£52.99.</p>
<p>Bethesda and Nintendo announced the news with a new gameplay trailer, which you can see below.</p>

<figure>
